---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="Privacy policy for Magic of Cinema.">
  <h1 class="mb-4 font-display text-4xl font-extrabold md:text-5xl">Privacy</h1>
  <div class="prose-cinema">
    <p>
      Magic of Cinema is written by <strong>MovieMan</strong>, a pen name. The
      site does not publish his real name, location, age, school, or photos.
    </p>

    <h2>Comments</h2>
    <p>
      Comments are powered by <a href="https://giscus.app/">Giscus</a>, which
      uses GitHub Discussions. To leave a comment, you'll need a free GitHub
      account. Your comment is visible publicly on the relevant GitHub
      Discussion.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      No tracking pixels, no third-party analytics, no advertising. If basic
      analytics are added later (page views only, anonymized), this page will
      be updated.
    </p>

    <h2>Images</h2>
    <p>
      Movie posters and backdrops are sourced from <a href="https://www.themoviedb.org/">TMDb</a>{" "}
      under their terms of service. Any images uploaded directly to the site
      have their EXIF metadata stripped before publishing.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, an adult guardian can be reached via the comments
      on any post.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
